org.apache.poi.hssf.record

Class OldCellRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.OldCellRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericRecord
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OldFormulaRecord, OldLabelRecord 

    public abstract class OldCellRecord
extends java.lang.Object
implements GenericRecord
    Base class for all old (Biff 2 - Biff 4) cell value records (implementors of CellValueRecordInterface). Subclasses are expected to manage the cell data values (of various types).(所有旧（Biff 2 - Biff 4）单元格值记录（CellValueRecordSurface的实现者）的基本类别。期望子类来管理（各种类型的）单元格数据值。)
